# UI Component Patterns

## Component Library
- **Base Components**: [src/components/ui/](mdc:src/components/ui/) - shadcn/ui components
- **Custom Components**: [src/components/](mdc:src/components/) - dashboard-specific components

## Key Components
1. **Dashboard**: [src/components/Dashboard.tsx](mdc:src/components/Dashboard.tsx) - Main dashboard view
2. **Navbar**: [src/components/Navbar.tsx](mdc:src/components/Navbar.tsx) - Navigation and theme toggle
3. **FileManager**: [src/components/FileManager.tsx](mdc:src/components/FileManager.tsx) - File upload and management
4. **ChatAssistant**: [src/components/ChatAssistant.tsx](mdc:src/components/ChatAssistant.tsx) - AI chat interface
5. **KPISettingsPanel**: [src/components/KPISettingsPanel.tsx](mdc:src/components/KPISettingsPanel.tsx) - KPI configuration

## Design Patterns
1. **Accordion Layouts**: Expandable rows instead of cards
2. **Turkish Language**: All UI text in Turkish
3. **Dark/Light Theme**: ThemeContext integration
4. **Responsive Design**: Mobile-friendly layouts
5. **Loading States**: Skeleton loaders and spinners

## Styling Standards
- **CSS Framework**: Tailwind CSS
- **Component Library**: shadcn/ui
- **Theme**: Custom dark/light theme
- **Typography**: Turkish font support
- **Colors**: Consistent color palette

## Layout Structure
- Navigation bar with tabs
- Main content area with metrics
- Accordion-style data tables
- Floating chat assistant
- Settings panels

## Accessibility
- ARIA labels for screen readers
- Keyboard navigation support
- High contrast mode support
- Focus management
